Optimal Threshold Selection
•
Goal
● Balance precision and recall
● Reduce false alarms
Why not 0.50?
● Higher false positives
● More good customers flagged.
Why 0.55?
● Highest F1-score (0.55)
● Similar defaulter detection
● Fewer false positives.
Business Benefit
• Better credit approval decisions
• Balanced risk detection
